Package be.ac.umons.jsonschematools.generator.exploration Description

Contains a generator that produces documents by exhaustively exploring the JSON schema. With the default value handlers, the produced documents have abstracted values. For instance, integer values are all represented by the special symbol \I. See AbstractConstants for all abstract values, and the non-API documentation for more information.
